Requirements
------------
 * ghc 6.4
 * libgmp (for ghc)
 * wxhaskell 0.10 (darcs version for now)
 * wxWidgets 2.5 or 2.6 (for wxhaskell)
 * graphviz (for GUI) 

wxWidgets and wxhaskell
-----------------------
If you want to use Unicode, you'll need to compile wxWidgets and
wxhaskell with special options.  Please see
  http://wiki.loria.fr/wiki/GenI/Getting_GenI

Building geni
-------------
 runhaskell Setup.lhs configure
 runhaskell Setup.lhs build
 runhaskell Setup.lhs install
 macosx-app /usr/local/bin/geni

(Note: blind users or GUI abstainers can do 'make nogui')
